title: Episode 243: Forced Love (Feat. Usman “Sojaboy”)
itunes:title: Episode 243: Forced Love (Feat. Usman “Sojaboy”)
description:
90 Day Fiancé star, Sojaboy, joins the ladies of Lip Service during his quarantine and opens up about his relationship with his woman Lisa. He breaks down how they met, the challenges they face because of his music career, why he felt pressured to be with her, and much more. Sojaboy even opens up about his need for a child and how that can negatively affect his and Lisa’s relationship moving forward. Stay healthy and enjoy!
